g.text: Hubway is metro-Boston's public bike share program, with 1,600 bikes and 180 stations across Greater Boston area.People used Hubway more than 65,000 times in 2016.
Citation: Hubway, Mass.Gov, United State Environmental Protection Agency
This reduced more than 135 tons of greenhouse emissions over the whole year.One tree can absorb 16kg greenhouse gas per day.1 day Hubway = plant 23 trees.
